+ Compiling
    ghc my_prog.hs
** Compiling a multi-module program without invoking
** the make utility
    ghc --make my_prog1.hs ...

+ Invoking the interpreter
    ghci
** To load functions within a Haskell source file
** (my_prog.hs) into the interpreter
    :l my_prog
** To reload the functions (when, say, you change the code)
    :l my_prog 
    OR
    :r
